{% include 'header.twig' %}

<main id="notLogin">
    
<section id="blog_post">
    
    <div class="container">
    <h1 class="blog_section_title">✍️ Latest Blog Insights</h1>
<p class="blog_section_subtitle">Stay informed with our latest news & articles</p>

<style>
    .blog_section_title {
        font-size: 32px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #2ecc71;
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 30px;
        font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
    }

    .blog_section_subtitle {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #7f8c8d;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
</style>
    
        <div class="row mb-5">
            
            {% for blog in blogs %}
                        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-12">
                <div class="blog_wraper">
                    <div class="blog_img">
                        {% if blog["image_file"] %} 
                          <a href="/blog/{{ blog["blog_get"] }}">
                            <img src="{{blog["image_file"]}}" class="img-fluid" alt="{{ blog["title"] }}">
                          </a>
                        {% endif %} 
                    </div>
                    <div class="blog_content">
                        <h4>{{ blog["title"] }}</h4>
                        <div class="blog_content">
                            <p><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 30px;">{{ blog["content"] }}</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="blog_btn_wrap">
                        <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">Read More &gt;&gt;</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            {% endfor %}           
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container mt-5">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <div class="blog_wraper">
                    <div class="blog_img">
                        <img src="https://imarticus.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/diigtal-marketing.gif" class="img-fluid" alt="Power of Cross-Platform Promotion">
                    </div>
                    <div class="blog_content">
                        <h4>The Power of Cross-Platform Promotion: Expanding Your Brand’s Reach</h4>
                        <p>In today's fast-paced digital world, businesses are continuously looking for effective ways to expand their reach and connect with their target audiences. Cross-platform promotion has emerged as one of the most powerful strategies in digital marketing. By promoting your brand across multiple platforms, you can effectively reach a wider audience and create a cohesive brand experience that resonates with customers.</p>

                        <p>The key benefits of cross-platform promotion include:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>Increased Brand Visibility:</strong> Engaging with your audience across various platforms allows your brand to be seen by a larger and more diverse audience.</li>
                            <li><strong>Improved Customer Engagement:</strong> You can engage with customers on their preferred platforms, building stronger relationships and trust.</li>
                            <li><strong>Better Conversion Rates:</strong> Cross-platform promotion helps in driving traffic from multiple sources, resulting in increased conversions and sales.</li>
                        </ul>

                        <p>To make the most of cross-platform promotion, it's essential to ensure that your messaging and branding are consistent across all platforms, whether it's social media, your website, or other marketing channels. By creating a seamless experience for your customers, you can enhance brand loyalty and drive long-term success.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="blog_btn_wrap">
                        <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">Read More &gt;&gt;</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container mt-5">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <div class="blog_wraper">
                    <div class="blog_img">
